        <abstract> 
<p>Suggests change in a passage [in MS] of CL’s [<hi rend="italic">Antiquity of man</hi> (1863)] dealing with adaptations for travel.</p>  
<p>Comments on review of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> by F. W. Hutton [<hi rend="italic">Geologist</hi> (1861): 132–6, 183–8].</p> 
            <p>Emphasises importance of variability for natural selection.</p>
            <p>Discusses possiblity of intelligent causes in variation.</p>
        </abstract>
